com.intel.fightclub.dialog.queries.model

Enum DialogSensor

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<DialogSensor>
      • com.intel.fightclub.dialog.queries.model.DialogSensor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Queryable, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<DialogSensor>

    @Immutable
public enum DialogSensor
extends java.lang.Enum<DialogSensor>
implements Queryable
    This class describes sensors known by Dialog. IMPORTANT: Dialog codes as provided to the enum elements shouldn't be changed unless required by dialog files.
